
PopUp menus are free menus that can be opened anywhere on the screen. There is two way to control them:
user clics on the PopUp button, releases the mouse button, chooses an item and clics again on the mouse button.
user clics and maintains his pression, and the PopUp menu is closed when he releases the mouse button.

There is some PopUp menu with a scrolling function. In this case, the mouse pointer contains an arrow and you can make scroll the menu by moving the pointeur on the top or the bottom. 

